metadata.label: Contents
value: 6. fol. 81b-88a: Risālah fī al-masḥ ʻalá al-khuffayn.
7. fol. 101b-104a: Qawāʻid fī maʻrifat samt al-qiblah.
9. fol. 112b-115b: Jadwal aṭwāl al-bilād wa-ʻurūḍihā wa-inḥirāf qiblatihā ʻan niṣf al-nahār wa-jihat al-samt.
11. fol. 129b-131a: Risālah fī maʻrifat iṣṭilāḥāt misāḥat al-ashkāl wa-mā yataʻallaqu bi-hā.
12. fol. 145b-148b: Tasdīd al-ʻaqāʼid fī sharḥ Tajrīd al-qawāʻid.
